Package: indi-apogee
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libindi1, libapogee3
Description: INDI driver for Apogee CCDs and Filter Wheels
 INDI Driver for Apogee CCDs and Filter Wheels
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.

Package: indi-apogee-dbg
Architecture: any
Depends: indi-apogee (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: INDI driver for Apogee CCDs and Filter Wheels
 INDI Driver for Apogee CCDs and Filter Wheels
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.
 This package contains the debug symbols for the this driver, useful to investigate problems in INDI.
